- `SwiftCinemas/SwiftCinemasTests/MockHTTPTransport.swift`
- `SwiftCinemas/SwiftCinemasTests/MockResponseFixtures.swift`
- `SwiftCinemas/SwiftCinemasTests/MbooksServiceTests.swift`
- `SwiftCinemas/SwiftCinemasTests/LoginGatewayServiceTests.swift`
