- `SwiftCinemas/SwiftCinemasTests/VenueForMoviesIntegrationTests.swift` (replace/rewrite/remove placeholder content)

───────────────────────────────────────────────────
📊 Success Criteria
───────────────────────────────────────────────────

- [ ] `SwiftCinemas.xctestplan` executes `SwiftCinemasTests` by default.
- [ ] Service contract tests compile and pass without backend dependency.
- [ ] Optional live smoke tests are explicitly gated.
- [ ] Backend switch (`SWIFT_REST_BACKEND`) selects mocked vs real execution.
- [ ] Mock fixture mapping covers all listed core endpoints.
- [ ] Covered endpoints include all high-traffic booking/login calls listed above.
- [ ] Placeholder test code is removed from active suite.
- [ ] Failures clearly identify endpoint and contract mismatch.
